</li>
<li id="cite_note-17"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-17">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="/wiki/Kirundi_language" class="mw-redirect" title="Kirundi language">Kirundi</a>: <i lang="rn">Repuburika y’Uburundi</i><sup id="cite_ref-16" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-16">&#91;13&#93;</a></sup> <span class="IPA nowrap" lang="rn-Latn-fonipa"><a href="/wiki/Help:IPA" title="Help:IPA">&#91;u.βu.ɾǔː.ndi&#93;</a></span>; <a href="/wiki/Swahili_language" title="Swahili language">Swahili</a>: <i lang="sw">Jamuhuri ya Burundi</i>; <a href="/wiki/French_language" title="French language">French</a>: <i lang="fr">République du Burundi</i> <span class="IPA nowrap" lang="fr-Latn-fonipa"><a href="/wiki/Help:IPA/French" title="Help:IPA/French">&#91;buʁundi,<span class="wrap"> </span>byʁyndi&#93;</a></span></span>
</li>
