<li id="cite_note-white-53"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-white_53-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">White, Matthew. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://users.erols.com/mwhite28/warstat2.htm#Rwanda">Death Tolls for the Major Wars and Atrocities of the Twentieth Century: C. Burundi (1972–73, primarily Hutu killed by Tutsi) 120,000</a> <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20070609095015/http://users.erols.com/mwhite28/warstat2.htm#Rwanda">Archived</a> 9 June 2007 at the <a href="/wiki/Wayback_Machine" title="Wayback Machine">Wayback Machine</a></span>
